Instructions:

1) Download. 
   1.1)Use git clone or download the source code from GitHub.

2) Setup. 
   2.1) Make sure that Python, Maven, and Java are in your system path.
   2.2) Locate and run the setup.py file in main folder. Wait for the installation.
   2.3) You can now delete the src folder.

3) Running. 
   3.1) Locate and run the file main-test or test-base.py in target/python folder. Those files contains some example of using the current version
        of the assistant.


